job.title: Prasar Bharati Copy Editor Recruitment 2021 –  Apply offline for Various Vacancies in Gujarat
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • News Reader & Others

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by Prasar Bharati for the vacancies of News Reader. If you are finding a government job in Gujarat then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Gujarat, from 15.05.2021, and till 16.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Gujarat and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification to apply for Prasar Bharati News Reader posts in Gujarat:

  • To apply for a News Reader posts in Gujarat, your 12th, Diploma, Graduate  must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is the 15.05.2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 16.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 50  years old. 

Prasar Bharati News Reader Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for Prasar Bharati Copy Editor Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly download the application form there and easily start the application process for these vacancies in Gujarat. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of Prasar Bharati and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY Prasar Bharati
  • Print out the application form
  • Fill up the detailed ask in the application form by blue or black pen
  • Now send this application form to the address mentioned in the official notification
